<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Foreign Words Valid in Scrabble — Loanwords You Can Play</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">English is a magpie language — it borrows freely from every tongue it encounters. Many of those borrowed words are now valid in Scrabble dictionaries, giving you access to unusual letter combinations and high-scoring plays that most opponents won't expect.</p>

<p>From Arabic to Yiddish, Japanese to Hindi, thousands of loanwords have become legitimate Scrabble plays. Knowing them gives you a vocabulary edge that pure English speakers often miss — and many of these words use high-value tiles extremely well.</p>

